{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d7a2ce5cf6","title":"对第二届全国政协会议筹备情况简报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19a51a759b","index":0,"year":1954,"month":11,"day":18,"articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6063c1aeae","type":"title","text":"对第二届全国政协会议筹备情况简报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6"},{"id":"b6d766d883","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6"},{"id":"14cca606a1","type":"paragraph","text":"章程与名单\"数日内即宜大体确定，否则十二月二十日以前开会恐来不及。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6"},{"id":"8d64a53a34","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6"},{"id":"eaa767c101","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6"},{"id":"26e6b9f919","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]指中国人民政治协商会议组织章程和第二届全国政协委员名单。政协全国委员会工作会议1954年11月3日讨论筹备第二届政协问题的情况简报中说：关于修改政协组织章程的工作，一致同意不必另写共同纲领，在政协组织章程前面加总纲一章，并推定13人组成起草小组，于10日内提出初稿，交工作会议讨论。关于第二届全国政协的参加单位，一致同意定为29个，即11个党派，17个团体以及特别邀请人士。政协各参加单位的名额、由各单位根据实际情况和需要进行安排，不搞平均主义。各党派、团体的人选，于10日内提出名单草案，先交工作会议协商，并加以平衡。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6"}],"page":{"id":"cf218d474b","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d7a2ce5cf6","start":343,"end":343}}}},"__N_SSG":true}